The paper introduces a novel framework for image generation using multi-agent generative adversarial networks (GANs) that communicate through message passing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which is the primary focus of the paper. The paper also involves computer vision (cs.CV) as it deals with image generation. Additionally, the paper involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it aims to achieve artificial general intelligence. The paper also involves neural networks (cs.NE) as it uses GANs, which are a type of neural network. Lastly, the paper involves social and information networks (cs.SI) as it deals with agents communicating and sharing intelligence.
